# STAT outbox — probe trigger files and results land here.
# This directory is STAT-only. Never shared with FIELD (jubilant-bassoon).
#
# Trigger files:
#   .trigger-cf-api        → cf-api-probe.yml trigger
#   .trigger-post-probe    → post-probe.yml trigger
#   .post-probe-body.json  → POST body for post-probe
#   .post-probe-headers    → optional headers
#
# Result files (committed by CI with [skip ci]):
#   cf-result-{TS}.txt
#   post-result-{TS}.txt
